    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>[I]n nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/1986" key="#Princeps">Sico</persName> Dei previdentia
                        Beneventane provincie <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, motus omni potentis
                        Dei misericordia et pro redemptione anime nostre, suggerente gloriose
                        potestatis nostre <persName key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer"
                            ref="#people/3458">Radichis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer">referendarius</rs>
                        <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelis</rs> noster, concedimus in <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs key="#Monasteries"
                                >monasterio</rs> Beate Sophię</orgName>, ubi <persName
                            key="#Abbesses" ref="#people/1976">Arigisa</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatissa</rs> preesse videtur, omnis <rs
                            key="#Public_exactions #Tolls">portaticum</rs> quod ex ipso cenobio per
                        consuetudinem de <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs> seu <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >tritico</rs> vel omnia alimonia aut quamlibet rebus dare debetis
                        nostris <rs key="#Clusae/gates #Public_exactions">portarariis</rs> in
                        civitatem has Beneventanas tam de <rs key="#Public_exactions">domnicale</rs>
                        quam etiam de <rs key="#Slave">servis</rs> ipsius monasterii seu de <rs
                            key="#Freeborn">liberis hominibus</rs> inibi pertinentibus quibus in
                        prephata nostra civitatem suas miserint causas, ita ut nec a gastaldiis
                        nostris nęque portarariis aut quamlibet personam accipiantur, sed cunta que
                        annualiter ex ipso cenobio in predictam nostram civitatem missa fuerint sive
                        ab eius servis quam liberis hominibus, sicut supra statuimus, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Privileges #Exemption"
                            >sine omni datione</rs> inibi mittantur et habeantur et a nullis ex
                        nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldiis, vel a quibuscumque
                        agentibus habeant requisitionem custodes prephati monasterii vel hii alii,
                        sed amodo et perpetuis temporibus ea que nunc concessimus ibidem securiter
                        possideantur. Quod vero preceptus concessionis ex iussionis nominate
                        potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/3460"
                            >Leo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actus <placeName ref="#places/3458"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Residential #Public_exactions #Exemption"
                            >Saba</placeName> quinto anno, [*******] mense augustu, quarta decima
                        indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
